    org.conqat.lib.commons.clone.IDeepCloneable

    public class SimulinkEncodedDataUtil
extends SimulinkBlock
    Util class to work with the data provided by MatResource and MatData sections (that usually appear in mdl files). The encoding is similar to UUencode, but not the same: There are no line breaks and no pre or suffixes. However, space characters (' ') need to be replaced by '`'. This class removes escaping from special characters.
